{"id":147371,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/韩国在争议岛屿部署固定火箭炮系统/","date":"2011-04-25T08:30:19Z","modified":"2011-04-25T08:30:19Z","title":"韩国在争议岛屿部署固定火箭炮系统","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">首尔</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据韩国媒体报道，韩国武装力量在与朝鲜有争议海上边界附近的两座岛屿上部署固定多管火箭炮系统，以防御来自北方的可能的攻击。《朝鲜日报》周一（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）援引政府圈内人士报道说，韩国在位于黄海的延坪（</span><span>Yeonpyeong</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）和白翎（</span><span>Baengnyeong</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）两座岛屿上部署了十多个“九龙（</span><span>Kuryong</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）”多管火箭炮。该型火箭炮可同时发射</span><span>36</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">枚火箭弹，射程</span><span>36</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">公里。韩国联合通讯社也作了相关报道。去年</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月，朝鲜军队炮击延坪岛，导致</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人丧生，毁坏众多建筑。事件发生后，韩国增加了对海上边界附近地区的</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">座岛屿上的军力。白翎岛是距边界线最近的岛屿。黄海边界是</span><span>1953</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年朝鲜战争结束后由美国领导的联合国军单方划定，朝鲜方面迄今不予承认。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15027941%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE%E5%B2%9B%E5%B1%BF%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%81%AB%E7%AE%A